# VK-Botting [![Documentation Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/vk-botting/badge/?version=latest)](https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest) This is a basic package for building async VK bots.
It is in early stages of development so it can be buggy.
That is also why it does not have full documentation atm.
Partial docs are available at https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/ru/latest (Russian) or https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/en/latest (English)

# VK-Botting

[![Documentation Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/vk-botting/badge/?version=latest)](https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest)

This is a basic package for building async VK bots.<br> It is in early stages of development so it can be buggy.<br> That is also why it does not have full documentation atm.<br> Partial docs are available at https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/ru/latest (Russian) or https://vk-botting.readthedocs.io/en/latest (English)
